nodes.text: The scalefish were group of fish species native to the planet Naboo. They were thought to be mostly harmless, bar the mee, which possessed poisonous spines, and the faa which was a vicious carnivore. Other species included doo, laa, ray, see, and tee. Many colorful varieties of scalefish lived in Lake Paonga around the city of Otoh Gunga.
